author: Brendan Cole
title: #FloridaMorons Trends as People Flock to the Beach after Coronavirus Restrictions Lifted in Parts of the State
description: Duval County beaches reopened on Friday afternoon, but with restricted hours and activities.
content:
People took to social media to express their anger at the decision to reopen some beaches in Florida following weeks of coronavirus restrictions.
